criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  above 18 years old;

          -  single tubular (tract length >2 cm) ECF;

          -  low output volume (<200 ml/24h);

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  fistulas of cancer-infiltrated;

          -  associated abscess;

          -  foreign bodies;

          -  distal bowel obstruction;
